imageAssets.description: A stylized, isometric illustration of a simple, initial beehive. It should be dark-themed, with subtle amber or gold accents, showing a basic wooden structure with a few hexagonal honeycombs visible. The overall mood should be calm and inviting. Digital art style.
imageAssets.purpose: Initial beehive visual for the main game area.

imageAssets.description: A stylized, isometric illustration of an expanded beehive. It should be dark-themed, with more intricate details, possibly showing multiple levels or extensions, and more visible honeycombs. Subtle amber or gold accents. Digital art style, consistent with the initial beehive.
imageAssets.purpose: First expanded beehive visual for the main game area, unlocked via upgrade.

imageAssets.description: A stylized, isometric illustration of a fully upgraded, advanced beehive. It should be dark-themed, highly detailed, perhaps with glowing elements, advanced structures, and a sense of prosperity and high production. Subtle amber or gold accents. Digital art style, consistent with previous beehives.
imageAssets.purpose: Second expanded beehive visual for the main game area, representing a high-tier upgrade.
